	   <tr><td colspan=2>Level 7-9 I would also reccomend the orc camps in the commons, or if you started in qeynos blackburrow is a good dungeon up to about lvl 14 or so, haven't hunted there in a long time but I remember there being a lot of trains there.<br><br>For the lvl 9-13 levels I decided to head to the wisp island between erudin and qeynos, there is normally not many people there and 2 spawn points for wisps. Keep all your greater lightstones you get there, by doing the concordance quest you can easily make 100-200pp in greater lightstones alone through these levels.<br><br>Level 13-18 you could also get a group at the orc highway, just make sure you get a good group, I've had several groups here that didn't know what they were doing and the exp was either very slow or you would find yourself constantly running for the zone. However a solid group here can do very well. <br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
